Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.42,0:02:12.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you betray me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shall now pay for what\nyou have done unto me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.75,0:02:39.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.22,0:02:46.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Full frontal nudity!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin, don't be such a fool!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.52,0:03:23.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you\nso excited about?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.93,0:03:24.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've done well!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We got the female flute back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.13,0:03:31.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.53,0:03:34.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The man on the scroll\nlooked just like Hidemasa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There could be a deep\nconnection between the two.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There must be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God! Oh my God!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No mistaking it.\NThis is Danjo's female flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was about 400-years-ago...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.77,0:04:09.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Shikima asked the\NMido clan to find the flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.40,0:04:13.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One of two flutes they've been\ndesperately searching for.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,400-years-ago?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was when Oda Nobunaga\nruled.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.78,0:04:17.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,fought for supremacy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.12,0:04:26.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there was an evil man called\NDanjo Matsunaga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He betrayed Nobunaga and hid\nin the Yamato mountains.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.06,0:04:32.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.83,0:04:37.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He poisoned the owner\nof his refuge and led a revolt.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He subjugated Yoshiteru, the\NAshikaga Shogun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and burned down the hall\nof the great Buddha.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.70,0:04:46.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He had even gained supremacy\nover all of Kyoto.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Shikima that\nhelped Danjo in his quest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.95,0:05:00.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo, indulging in some\ndebauchery as usual.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gamara!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've come from the Shikima\nrealm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.53,0:05:12.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to make a request\nof you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time I need your help.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anything to humiliate\NNobunaga...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.24,0:05:19.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and take control away\nfrom him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed evil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of launching\na coup in the Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and taking the title of King\nfor myself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gamara!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.79,0:05:33.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This evening, I will kill your\nson Kyoshiro Karimara...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and take Shanahime from\nthe Karimara fortress.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:37.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.23,0:05:43.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was a young man\ncalled Kyoshiro Karimara...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...whose blood was the\nmelding of two realms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The product of Danjo\nand his wife...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.50,0:05:53.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who had been offered to\nhim by the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's late!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.08,0:06:00.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, will Shanahime come\nto this fortress as my bride?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must be patient, Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is an agreement between\nyour father and the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As one who carries the line of\NDanjo and the Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.99,0:06:13.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you will no doubt be the\nsupreme ruler of this world...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...when you receive\NShanahime of the royal line...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...said to be the most beautiful\nof the 3,000 realms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it worries you, just play\nthis male flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime will respond to you\nwith her female flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.09,0:06:48.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the male and female Danjo\nflutes are love flutes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The beautiful lady that came\nto Hidemasa's house was...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime of 400-years-ago.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An ancient curse must have\ncalled upon her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.57,0:07:01.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa said he was cleaning\nout the storehouse...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...when he came across the\nmale flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He must have played it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how he called\NShanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Hidemasa from the\NMatsunaga family?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.65,0:07:16.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He must be a descendant of\NDanjo, or rather Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.13,0:07:22.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kyoshiro was killed at\nthe Karimara fortress...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:25.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...before he could\npass on his seed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.71,0:07:35.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.79,0:07:46.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet sound of\nthe female flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.59,0:07:47.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo, have you\nlost your mind?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.04,0:08:09.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You killed Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With poison coursing through\nyour body...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you won't be displaying that\nrenowned skill of yours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To betray the royal line.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have joined forces with\NShanahime...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.96,0:09:00.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who's ambition is to\ncontrol the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.76,0:09:03.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You... you treacherous\nbastard!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to die.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.37,0:09:16.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot let you take\nreign over the world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.31,0:09:18.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will make Shanahime mine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die, my son!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed me, Shanahime!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.78,0:09:48.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Killing your own wife and son\nto further your ambition!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What Shanahime did\nwas unforgivable!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:58.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why would she join\nforces with evil...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to fight against the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.72,0:10:04.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime was betrayed\nby the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.19,0:10:05.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only possibility.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.53,0:10:10.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was the Shikima King, my\nfather, alive back then?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.57,0:10:15.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was just before he\ntook control of the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one who becomes King\ncan live 1 ,000 years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.24,0:10:24.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When the previous king died\nand the throne was empty...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Shikima began to\nsplinter apart.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is the\NAnti-Shikima?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.18,0:10:32.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a branch that\nwas destroyed...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...at the hands of your father.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.42,0:10:39.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, that man in the scroll.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Does he resemble this man?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.73,0:10:49.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The image on the scroll is\NKyoshiro Karimara...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.30,0:10:52.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who died 400-years-ago,\nfull of hatred.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime was also calling\nhim Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:04.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, Shanahime is trying to\nbring Kyoshiro back to life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.29,0:11:07.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa is the necessary\nsacrifice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She'll return to take away\nthe female flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the male flute is at\NHidemasa's house!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.80,0:11:17.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to find her and\nget Hidemasa back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.93,0:11:20.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime has powers...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...beyond our understanding.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.55,0:11:34.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin? Where are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.68,0:11:39.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Excuse me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hidemasa in?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's Hidemasa's\ngirlfriend or something?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And who are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sayoko, his cousin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.27,0:11:58.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When I spoke with him,\nhe said he was feeling ill.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.14,0:12:00.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I came to check on him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa isn't here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.58,0:12:03.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.71,0:12:05.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.78,0:12:09.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I found this tea kettle with\nthe flute, up in the storehouse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seemed important so I\nbrought it along.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,-The Spider Kettle!\N-Huh?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.99,0:12:18.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Spider Kettle I'd\nasked Hidemasa to find.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.69,0:12:21.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unusual tea kettle from\nthe Tensho Era.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.57,0:12:26.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You may fool others...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but you can't deceive us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're trained in the ways\nof the Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.28,0:12:39.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll slice his throat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.02,0:12:45.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've revealed yourself!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.83,0:12:59.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You hellish beast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will take your lives,\nalong with the female flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be warned!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.38,0:13:11.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She got away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flute that causes\NFather to suffer!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, something about that tea\nkettle worries me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.03,0:13:28.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What if it creates another\ndisaster in the Shikima?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:30.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better go to\nthe Shikima for now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So Shanahime has taken the\NSpider Kettle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:40.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father, what is Shanahime\ntrying to do anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.71,0:13:43.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying desperately to\nbring Kyoshiro back to life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The old lady said...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.31,0:13:49.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that Kyoshiro died full\nof hatred for Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to clear her name.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.95,0:13:55.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's using the Anti-Shikima's\ntreasured Spider Kettle...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in an attempt\nto settle an old score.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, she didn't\nactually betray Kyoshiro?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.03,0:14:07.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was vying for succession to\nthe Shikima throne then.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.47,0:14:14.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bring news.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.84,0:14:16.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo has betrayed\nour arrangement...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and has killed Kyoshiro\nat Karimara!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NWhat about my sister?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.58,0:14:26.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Karimara has burned down\nand they're both dead.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, Gamara!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Find him! No matter where\nhe is!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo will pay for this too!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.96,0:14:36.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:41.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We tried desperately to bring\nback order to this realm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.40,0:14:46.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's when we joined forces\nwith the Mido clan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.81,0:14:54.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Karimara fortress is\nburning down!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.39,0:15:04.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Karimara fortress!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro! Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you've escaped somehow...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,please answer my flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me with your\nmale flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.24,0:15:25.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is unclear what misfortunes\nlater fell upon Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some say she drowned in a\nlake.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.19,0:15:36.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I was not able to hear\nthe truth from Danjo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever Nobunaga may do...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.67,0:15:54.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I have the power of\nthe Shikima behind me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give up the\NSpider Kettle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.59,0:16:05.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If I drink the kettle's\nsecret potion...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll become immortal\nand acquire magical powers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will never give it up\nto Nobunaga!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Shikima\nhas forsaken you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo perished at Shigisan\NCastle in Yamato.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:39.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is thought that the\NSpider Kettle...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.02,0:16:43.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...coveted by Nobunaga, was\nalso destroyed in the fire.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that was not true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So in all the confusion,\nthe Spider Kettle was saved?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.96,0:16:49.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But for the past 400 years,\nno one knew what came of it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.37,0:16:57.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those who revolted were\ndeemed the Anti-Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and they were all destroyed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But along with the curse, the\NSpider Kettle had vanished.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.38,0:17:07.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So Shanahime got hold of the\namorous tea kettle?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.58,0:17:11.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of the tea kettle will\nbe used...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.85,0:17:13.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring Kyoshiro back to\nlife.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.19,0:17:17.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must stop Shanahime!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.36,0:17:21.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is not of the real world.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:24.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To preserve her youth and\nkeep her human form...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.20,0:17:27.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...she'll destroy many women\nto use their bodies!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.47,0:17:32.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko, you must draw her out\nwith that female flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.21,0:17:36.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...but this is the flute that\ncauses you so much suffering!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.21,0:17:40.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bear it, if it means\nputting her to rest forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.92,0:17:50.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maria! Your Majesty!\NI promise to look after Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,-Thank you!\N-Fubuki.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.30,0:17:59.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Guards! Protect the two from\nthe curse of the Anti-Shikima!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Help them find Shanahime!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.37,0:18:02.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:08.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear they found a\nmummy in the locker room?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck! That's gross!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's Kimie or Sanae.\NThey're still missing, right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a predicament!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that fragrance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from over there!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.42,0:18:50.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.86,0:19:02.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The night is ours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited for you\nover 400 years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was called by\nyour male flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.31,0:19:17.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one who called me\nback to this world...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.81,0:19:22.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...was one who so resembles\nyou, Hidemasa Matsunaga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.25,0:19:27.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is you, and yet it's not you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But finally,\nthe Spider Kettle is mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will sacrifice this\NHidemasa...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with the power\nof the Anti-Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring you back to life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My body is so...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my body is so on fire\nfor you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:16.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the curse of the\NAnti-Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the power of this\NSpider Kettle...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.15,0:20:29.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I will bring you to life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.05,0:20:34.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mummies at the college?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She sucked the life out of\NKimie and Sanae...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to hang on to her\nown youth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And to think I was right there!\NThis is awful!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.97,0:20:53.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!\NThis isn't the time for crying!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.67,0:20:57.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We must concentrate all our\NShikima abilities...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:20:59.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...to track down Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki.\NCan you hear anything?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.90,0:21:23.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki's taken the Shikima\nform, to be more vigilant.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The call of the water fowl!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.70,0:21:40.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro's double.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.07,0:21:42.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.21,0:21:51.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.39,0:22:08.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The park.\NTowards the Water Park!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.16,0:22:45.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.91,0:22:56.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Feel my passion!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.27,0:23:31.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the male flute! Come on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.55,0:23:46.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who plays my flute?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.39,0:23:49.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.36,0:23:51.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.16,0:23:53.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear it anymore.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.86,0:23:55.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You go that way!\NI'll head this way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.07,0:23:56.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.90,0:23:58.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.38,0:24:12.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro, it's me!\NIt's Shanahime!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.15,0:24:14.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.10,0:24:28.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime! You betrayed me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.50,0:24:30.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.20,0:24:33.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I implore you!\NListen to what I have to say!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.10,0:24:35.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.21,0:24:38.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed my mother\nand I. Puppet of evil.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.18,0:24:41.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot forgive you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.91,0:24:46.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.79,0:24:51.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.93,0:24:59.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That cry...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.17,0:25:08.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shall be purged from all\nexistence...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.64,0:25:11.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...along with the Shikima\nwho destroyed me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.88,0:25:16.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die, Shanahime.\NYou treacherous beast!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.88,0:25:21.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no love for you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.35,0:25:24.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.36,0:25:29.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic fool!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.50,0:25:40.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:42.24,0:25:44.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki!\NHear that splashing sound?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.78,0:25:49.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I heard a woman's\ncry just before that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.28,0:25:52.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A victim! Shanahime must be\nsomewhere in this park!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.28,0:25:53.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Play the female flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.68,0:25:56.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all we have\nto draw her out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.97,0:26:13.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko! What's that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.27,0:26:15.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro Karimara!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.77,0:26:18.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's come back!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.34,0:26:23.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That flute!\NStop playing that flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.79,0:26:36.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:51.94,0:26:52.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.48,0:27:00.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.65,0:27:03.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.83,0:27:16.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.50,0:27:21.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy the Shikima\nfrom all of existence.
